aa(lp235
VA similar demographic of women in Jennie's area
p236
aVwho gave birth at the same hospital her clients did
p237
aVwere three times more likely to give birth
p238
aVto a baby below a healthy weight.
p239
aVJennie is making headway into what has been seen for decades
p240
aVas an almost intractable problem.
p241
aVSome of you might be thinking,
p242
aVall this one-on-one attention that The JJ Way requires
p243
aVmust be too expensive to scale.
p244
aVWell, you'd be wrong.
p245
aVThe visit with the provider is not the center of Jennie's model,
p246
